美国在一次性技术突破上向来得心应手——原子弹、太空竞赛莫不如此。
The US had become great at singular technological breakthroughs, the atom bomb, the space race.

273
00:15:46,640 --> 00:15:48,533
高铁也被视为
High-speed rail was considered

